videos.headline: Georgia Tech recovers as Virginia Tech fumbles away opening kickoff
videos.description: Harrison Butker kickoff for 64-yards, Der'Woun Greene return for 37-yards to the VTech 38 Der'Woun Greene fumbled, forced by Terrell Lewis, recovered by GTech Nate Cottrell

videos.headline: Lawrence Austin picks off Jerod Evans pass in the end zone
videos.description: Jerod Evans pass intercepted, touchback. Lawrence Austin return for no gain

videos.headline: Matthew Jordan keeps it, races 53-yards to the house
videos.description: Matthew Jordan run for 53-yards for a TD (Harrison Butker KICK)

videos.headline: Jordan lowers the shoulder and powers through for his second score of the game
videos.description: Matthew Jordan run for 3-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Virginia Tech recovers after botched snap by Georgia Tech
videos.description: TEAM run for 1-yard to the GTech 26 TEAM fumbled, recovered by VTech Anthony Shegog

videos.headline: Virginia Tech gets on the board with diving catch by Isaiah Ford
videos.description: Jerod Evans pass complete to Isaiah Ford for 5-yards for a TD

videos.headline: Lawrence Austin picks off Jerod Evans for the second time today
videos.description: Jerod Evans pass intercepted Lawrence Austin return for 3-yards to the GTech 32

videos.headline: Hokies' Rogers makes sensational one-handed catch
videos.description: Virginia Tech TE Sam Rogers makes a great one-handed catch for a 9-yard gain in the fourth quarter against Georgia Tech.

videos.headline: Lawrence Austin rips the ball away, forcing his third Virginia Tech turnover of the game.
videos.description: Jerod Evans pass complete to Bucky Hodges for 11-yards Bucky Hodges fumbled, forced by Lawrence Austin, recovered by GTech Lance Austin

videos.headline: Georgia Tech secures upset with 56-yard TD run
videos.description: Already up on No. 14 Virginia Tech, Georgia Tech keeps piling it on when Marcus Marshall goes right up the middle for a 56-yard touchdown run to put the Yellow Jackets up 30-7.

videos.headline: Hokies QB Evans powers his way into the end zone
videos.description: Jerod Evans run for 8-yards for a TD (Joey Slye KICK)

videos.headline: Evans barrels over Ga Tech lineman for 2nd score
videos.description: Jerod Evans run for 7 yds for a TD, 2-pt conversion attempt fails.
